          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "INTAD"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " With reasonably high statistical accuracy",
                " the reaction cross section simultaneously have been",
                " measured at five laboratory angles between 30 and",
                " 142 degrees. Differential cross sections were",
                " obtained by comparing the He-4(g,n)He-3 and",
                " H-2(g,n)H-1 cross sections. The latter were obtained",
                " from alternating runs with D(2)O and H(2)O in an",
                " identical target configuration as that used for",
                " helium. for the deuterium cross section, the",
                " experimental results were normalized to the",
                " calculation of Partovi. Differential cross sections",
                " were used to obtain the total cross section."
              ]
            }
          ],
